OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRobin Parkinson: 'Allo     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'Allo! and Button Moon     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Factor dies at 92           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Actor Robin Parkinson, known for his   
OL,6, roles in TV sitcoms like 'Allo 'Allo!  
OL,7, and as the narrator of children's show 
OL,8, Button Moon, has died at the age of 92.
OL,10,FParkinson played Monsieur Ernest       
OL,11,FLeclerc, a regular in 'Allo 'Allo! in  
OL,12,F1991 and 92.                           
OL,14,FCo-star Vicki Michelle paid tribute,   
OL,15,Fdescribing him as "a truly lovely man".
OL,17,FThe actor was also a familiar face for 
OL,18,Fhis appearances in comedies including  
OL,19,FDad's Army, The Young Ones, Rising     
OL,20,FDamp, Hi-de-Hi! and The Two Ronnies.   
